text: Stefania Świerzy (19 June 1934 - 11 June 2020) was a Polish gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ruda Śląska
